Package environment

Class CellPerception

  • java.lang.Object
    • environment.CellPerception
  • public class CellPerception
extends java.lang.Object
    A class of representations of positions in a Perception. A CellPerception is part of a Perception and has a vector of all Representations of items on that coordinate.
